          [
            84.0,
            1229.0
          ]
        ]
      },
      {
        "block_label": "text",
        "block_content": "The Impact of Diffusion Steps We adjust the diffusion step t to examine its impact on the results. The experiments are conducted using the DDIM model on CIFAR-10 with diffusion steps for inference. The outcomes are presented in Figure 4. Our findings indicate that as long as a moderate step is chosen, the attack performance remains excellent, demonstrating that our algorithm is not sensitive to the choice of t. This further underscores the robustness of our algorithm. We also plot the change of diffusion step",
        "block_bbox": [
          82,
