      {
        "block_label": "figure_title",
        "block_content": "Figure 4: The impact of diffusion steps on DDIM. We train a DDIM model on the CIFAR-10 dataset and use different diffusion steps for inference. We find that high accuracy can be achieved as long as a moderate step number is chosen. This opens up possibilities for practical applications in real-world scenarios.",
        "block_bbox": [
          618,
